rows.label: qst003206_msg0001
rows.name:
Bonono?! Bonono!
Thank God you're alive!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0002
rows.name:
Bonono was almost not so alive!
If friends show up later, Bonono
probably monster food.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0003
rows.name: Was quite thrilling experience.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0004
rows.name:
Especially flying from Acedia!
That probably new record flight
distance of Nopon!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0005
rows.name:
Not get thrills like that every day!
Bonono kind of want to try again!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0006
rows.name: ...Please don't do that...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0007
rows.name: Alulu never want to fall like that again...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0008
rows.name: Who's this girl?

rows.label: qst003206_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh, this Alulu-chan. She fall from Acedia
to World Tree together with Bonono.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0010
rows.name:
Alulu thought would die when crash
into World Tree. But landed on Bonono
instead. Nice and fluffy landing.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0011
rows.name:
Wow...you totally saved her life!
I guess you did something cool
for once there, Bonono.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0012
rows.name: What Aki mean by "for once"?!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0013
rows.name:
Then when Alulu get attacked by
monsters, Bonono run away faster
than legs can carry Bonono.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0014
rows.name: Urk...

rows.label: qst003206_msg0015
rows.name:
Meanwhile Alulu make new Blade
friend and bash up three monsters!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0016
rows.name:
Wow... Alulu-chan 
you're way cooler than Bonono.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0017
rows.name: Ooh, friend Aki make Alulu blush!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0018
rows.name:
W-well, important thing is everyone
safe now! Happy end for all!

rows.label: qst003206_msg0019
rows.name:
Yeah, I guess that's true.
We should be thanking these
brave Drivers.

rows.label: qst003206_msg0020
rows.name: Thank friends very very much!
